---
/** Vista única en viewports &lt; md: la app completa está pensada para escritorio. */
---

<div
  class="md:hidden fixed inset-0 z-[120] flex flex-col bg-linear-to-b from-white via-gray-50/90 to-indigo-50/40 dark:from-gray-950 dark:via-gray-950 dark:to-indigo-950/30 overflow-y-auto overscroll-y-contain"
  data-mobile-landing-screen
  role="document"
  aria-label="SkillAtlas — vista móvil"
>
  <div class="flex flex-col flex-1 items-center justify-center px-6 py-12 text-center max-w-md mx-auto w-full min-h-[min(100dvh,100%)]">
    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200/90 dark:border-gray-800 bg-white/80 dark:bg-gray-900/80 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 shadow-sm">
      <span class="inline-flex h-2 w-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-500 shadow-[0_0_10px_rgba(16,185,129,0.5)]" aria-hidden="true"></span>
      SkillAtlas
    </div>
    <h1 class="mt-6 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 leading-snug" data-i18n="mobileLanding.title">
      Pensado para pantallas grandes
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="mobileLanding.body">
      El tablero, el CV y el portfolio están optimizados para ratón y teclado. En móvil te dejamos solicitar acceso o entrar si ya tienes cuenta.
    </p>
    <div class="mt-10 flex flex-col gap-3 w-full">
      <a
        href="/request-access"
        class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-gray-900 dark:bg-gray-100 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-white dark:text-gray-900 no-underline hover:opacity-95"
        data-i18n="mobileLanding.ctaAccess"
      >
        Solicitar acceso
      </a>
      <a
        href="/login"
        class="inline-flex w-full items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-gray-300/90 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white/90 dark:bg-gray-900/90 px-4 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 no-underline hover:bg-gray-50 dark:hover:bg-gray-800"
        data-i18n="mobileLanding.ctaLogin"
      >
        Ya tengo cuenta
      </a>
    </div>
    <p class="mt-10 text-xs text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-500 leading-relaxed" data-i18n="mobileLanding.footer">
      Vuelve desde un ordenador para el mapa de skills, proyectos y portfolio.
    </p>
  </div>
</div>
